## Summary
Notivize is a no-code platform for product engagement notifications that integrates with Amplitude for cohort syncing. The documentation details the setup process requiring an API key from Notivize's settings and explains how to configure the destination in Amplitude Data and export cohorts with customizable sync cadence.

